install Gazebo (any version should work. I am using the 7.15.0)
Follow: 
http://wiki.ros.org/kinetic/Installation/Ubuntu

type (while in the workspace):  
catkin_make
then type: 
roslaunch mybot_gazebo mybot_world.launch

To make the robot have our proggramed behavior type: 
rosrun beginner_tutorials listener

The environment currently is one made so we could test the behavior of the robot. Feel free to change the
environment by changing the mybot.world file in /mybot_ws/src/mybot_gazebo/worlds




